#  Amazon Mobile App – Bug Report (Markdown Version)
1. Bug Title

Customer photo/video does not open in full screen; screen freezes.

2. Environment

Device: iQOO Neo 10R

OS: Android

App: Amazon Shopping

Network: WiFi/Mobile Data


3. Module

Product Detail Page → Customer Reviews (Photos & Videos section)

4. Severity

High

5. Priority

Medium

6. Preconditions

A product with customer-uploaded photos/videos must exist.

7. Steps to Reproduce

Open the Amazon mobile application.

Search for any product.

Open the product detail page.

Scroll down to Customer Reviews with Photos/Videos.

Tap on any customer-uploaded image or video.

Observe the behavior of the screen.

8. Expected Result

The selected media should open in full screen.

User should be able to zoom, swipe, play video, and close the view.

9. Actual Result

Full screen does NOT open.

Screen becomes stuck/frozen.

No touch controls work (Back button, swipe, close).

User must minimize or force-close the app.

10. Impact

Users cannot view product quality media.

Affects buying decisions.

Poor user experience.

11. Attachments

